data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. This beautiful, updated home brings comfort and appeal together.  Built in 1973, the home features 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, providing ample room for your family to grow and create amazing memories.   The home's interior offers a warm and welcoming atmosphere, as you will notice the natural light flowing through the open space of the kitchen and living room with gorgeous granite counter tops, and new wood-look slip resistant tile floors, and fresh paint throughout. There are also new interior doors and light fixtures to give the home that special touch.   The lovely barn door leads you to the spacious bonus room and screened in patio where you can relax while the children run around the generous-sized fenced in backyard.   Located in Polk County, the home is conveniently situated for access to local amenities and attractions. With no monthly association fees, a newer roof, and A/C unit, this property offers low ongoing costs and peace of mind.   This single-family residence offers a charming and practical layout, perfect for both living and potential investment purposes. Whether you're a first-time homebuyer, a growing family, or an investor looking for a solid property in a desirable location, this home, is certainly worth considering.
